“Amen Break”
@VirgilAbloh captures his new #LouisVuitton collection in a film exploring ideas of transmission: the act of passing on something from one person to another and activating waves of change across generations. The film is metaphorically informed by the little-known drum break of the same name that would become a founding factor in hip-hop and jungle music.

Featuring #SaulWilliams, #IssaPerica, #KandisWilliams, #GZA, #CalebFemi, #ShabakaHutchings, #LupeFiasco,#JulianWilliams, and #Goldie, alongside a broad cast of talent.

See more from the show at louisvuitton.com

A Film by @virgilabloh

Starring @yasiinbey, @saulwilliams, @malikee and @kai_isaiah_jamal
